'''水果凝乳'''（{{lang-en|Fruit curd}}）是一種用[[檸檬|檸檬]]<ref name="lemon">{{cite web | title = Lemon curd | publisher = BBC | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_curd_68499 | accessdate = 2015-01-08 | archive-date = 2015-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150109222056/http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_curd_68499 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[青檸|青檸]]<ref name="lime">{{cite web | title = Fresh lime curd | publisher = BBC | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/freshlimecurd_4555 | accessdate = 2015-01-08 | archive-date = 2015-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150110165000/http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/freshlimecurd_4555 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[橙子|橙子]]<ref name="orange">{{cite web | title = Orange curd | publisher = Time Inc. | url = http://www.foodandwine.com/recipes/orange-curd | accessdate = 2015-01-08 | archive-date = 2015-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150109032855/http://www.foodandwine.com/recipes/orange-curd | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[橘子|橘子]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/NECTARINE-LIME-CURD-TART-WITH-A-BROWN-SUGAR-CRUST-15128 |title=Nectarine lime curd tart with a brown-sugar crust |publisher=Gourmet Magazine |date=June 1998 |accessdate=2008-09-02 |archive-date=2008-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915084734/http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/NECTARINE-LIME-CURD-TART-WITH-A-BROWN-SUGAR-CRUST-15128 |dead-url=no }}</ref>等[[柑橘類|柑橘類]]製作的點心。現在也有用[[百香果|百香果]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/PASSION-FRUIT-MERINGUE-TART-232181 |title=Passion-fruit meringue tart |publisher=Gourmet Magazine |date=June 2005 |accessdate=2008-09-02 |archive-date=2008-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203165523/http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/PASSION-FRUIT-MERINGUE-TART-232181 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[芒果|芒果]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/MANGO-CURD-5379 |title=Mango curd |publisher=Gourmet Magazine |date=June 1998 |accessdate=2008-09-02 |archive-date=2008-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803173202/http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/MANGO-CURD-5379 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[樹莓|樹莓]]<ref name="definitional">{{cite web |title=Cake Talk: What the terms mean |work=The Joy of Cooking |publisher=The Seattle Times |date=2005-06-29 |url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20050629&slug=caketerms29 |accessdate=2008-09-02 |archive-date=2008-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080603133149/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20050629&slug=caketerms29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[小紅莓|小紅莓]]、[[黑莓|黑莓]]<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.recipezaar.com/176302 |title=How to be a Domestic Goddess, Cranberry curd |author=Nigella Lawson |page=343 |publisher=Hyperion Books |isbn=0-7868-6797-3 |date=2001-11-14 |accessdate=2008-09-02}}</ref>製作。基本材料是[[蛋黃|蛋黃]]、[[砂糖|砂糖]]、果汁、果皮。做法是將這些原料在一起煮之後冷卻形成凝膠狀物質即可<ref name="recipe">{{cite news |author=Gordon Ramsay |title=Lemon and Poppy Seed Scones with Homemade Lemon Curd |publisher=The Times |date=2007-06-20 |accessdate=2008-07-13}}</ref>。

在19世紀末至20世紀初，在傳統的英國下午茶中的自製檸檬凝乳是以[[麵包|麵包]]或者[[司康餅|司康餅]]作為[[果醬|果醬]]的替代品，並當作[[蛋糕|蛋糕]]、[[糕點|糕點]]或[[塔|塔]]<ref name="tradition">{{cite web |last=D'Sa |first=Elaine M. |date=August 2004 |title=Preparing and Preserving Lemon Curd |publisher=The University of Georgia |url=http://www.uga.edu/nchfp/publications/nchfp/factsheets/lemoncurd.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2016-10-31 |archive-date=2012-05-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67NMQUlpl?url=http://nchfp.uga.edu/publications/nchfp/factsheets/lemoncurd.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

